channel.title: Multiple people working on a rsps?
channel.description:
Is it possible to have more than one person code a server? Like my friend lives in lebbanon, and he goes to school when i am going to bed, so it is perfect for working on a server, twice the coding gets done.
So can i like send him the source and he can code,
But how do i get the stuff he coded without having to download it?
Thanks in advance!!

item.title: Multiple people working on a rsps?
item.dc:creator: @RiiPiiNFtW RiiPiiNFtW
item.description:
@RiiPiiNFtW wrote:

No, when you share a folder with a partner the certain files are updated every time they’re shared and they are replaced by a new upload of the file to the partner(s) who didn’t save.
